  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/COPI_0000248">
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="en">A diaphragm actuator is an actuator that uses a diaphragm as an essential component for converting control signals into mechanical motion or force to operate other equipment.</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="pt-br">Um atuador de diafragma é um atuador que utiliza um diafragma como componente essencial para converter sinais de controle em movimento mecânico ou força para operar outros equipamentos.</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <iof-av:primitiveRationale xml:lang="en">Classification basis is constructive - identity given by diaphragm mechanism. Under OWA, sufficient conditions would force any equipment with a diaphragm component to be classified as a diaphragm actuator, potentially including complex hybrid systems or custom equipment where the diaphragm serves auxiliary functions. Starting with necessary conditions protects against such false positives.</iof-av:primitiveRationale>
    <iof-av:isPrimitive rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</iof-av:isPrimitive>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/construct/MaterialArtifact"/>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:nodeID="n77c2a26f99c94a33993b8edf520dd96cb931"/>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/COPI_0000207"/>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">diaphragm actuator</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="pt-br">atuador de diafragma</rdfs:label>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">[ISO 15926-4] A &lt;DIAPHRAGM ACTUATOR&gt; is an &lt;INSTRUMENTATION ITEM&gt; and a &lt;CONTROLLED ACTUATOR&gt; that is using a &lt;DIAPHRAGM&gt;</skos:definition>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"/>
    <iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom xml:lang="en">∀x(DiaphragmActuator(x) → (Actuator(x) ∧ ∃y(Diaphragm(y) ∧ hasComponentPartAtAllTimes(x,y))))</iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom>
    <iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom xml:lang="en">DiaphragmActuator ⊑ Actuator ⊓ ∃hasComponentPartAtAllTimes.Diaphragm</iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom>
  </rdf:Description>
